node.text:
Introducing Friday Beers Smokebros. Every Wednesday we’ll be featuring the studliest of studs, hunkiest of hunks, and otherwise epic dudes. Today’s Smokebro is Jason Protass, 23, Austin, TX. He loves Dave’s Hot Chicken, batted .756 in little league, and wants to teach golf when he grows up. He can do 25 push-ups in a row. A graduate of University of Texas, Jason also told us, “He survives off of food.”

Nominate your bros by DMing @fb.smokebros 🤝
